      are welcome to join and learn meditation together, as well as meet other meditators.
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mt-4 px-4">
      <h5>Meditation for Relaxation</h5>
      <div class="text-muted">Beginner meditation classes</div>
      <div>Tuesday night</div>
      <div>7.00 - 8.30pm</div>
      <div>Difficulty: *</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mt-4 px-4">
      <h5>Buddhist Chanting and Meditation</h5>
      <div>Thursday night</div>
      <div>7.00 - 8.30pm</div>
      <div>Difficulty: **</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mt-4 px-4">
      <h5>Buddhist Wisdom and Meditation</h5>
      <div>Saturday night</div>
      <div>6.00 - 8.00pm</div>
      <div>Difficulty: **</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mt-4 px-4">
      <h5>Meditation via Zoom</h5>
      <div class="text-muted">Beginner meditation classes</div>
      <div>Saturday night</div>
      <div>7.00 - 8.20pm</div>
      <div>Difficulty: *</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 col-md-6 col-lg-4 mt-4 px-4">
      <h5>Weekend Meditation</h5>
      <div>Sunday</div>
      <div>2.30 - 4.00pm</div>
      <div>Difficulty: *</div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 text-center mt-3">
      <p>
        You can donate at your discretion via the link below<br>Sathu üôè
      </p>
      <form action="https://www.paypal.com/donate" method="post" target="_blank">
        <input type="hidden" name="hosted_button_id" value="2CYLN39RHDUVS" />
        <input type="image" src="https://www.paypalobjects.com/en_GB/i/btn/btn_donate_LG.gif" border="0" name="submit" title="PayPal - The safer, easier way to pay online!" alt="Donate with PayPal button" />
      </form>
      <img class="img-fluid mt-3" src="assets/images/teachings/paypal-qr-code.jpeg" alt="Paypal QR code" role="presentation">
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 mt-5 px-5 text-center text-muted">
      <div>* This class does not require any prior meditation experience. Everyone is welcome.</div>
      <div>** This class does require some meditation experience. You should have a good understanding of how to practice meditation.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row my-5">
    <div class="col-12 text-center">
      <LinkToAndScrollNav @route="teachings.meditation-benefits">
        <button type="button" class="btn btn-outline-primary">
          Learn more about the benefits
        </button>
      </LinkToAndScrollNav>
    </div>
  </div>
